{"tid":382250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【棋靈王召喚】鮑 起 靜 雀 戰 鄧 麗 欣 劉 嘉 玲 薛 家 燕","createTime":"2017-08-31T14:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T11:32:09.000Z","uid":24160,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7420c4be7ed43bf5b2a219f74e47bb6b8b9493a7","tid":382250,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170831/photo/bkn-20170831202851398-0831_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170831212841\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170831%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170831202851398-0831_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170831212841&h=05f6addb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170831/photo/bkn-20170831202851398-0831_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170831212841\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170831%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170831202851398-0831_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170831212841&h=5de804f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人鄧麗欣（Stephy）是導演葉念琛的愛將，近日她亦份為英皇電影《我的情敵女婿》演出其中一角，更在戲中與三位實力派演員劉嘉玲、鮑起靜和薛家燕同場較技，四人拍攝一場打麻雀戲，一較高下。<br />\n<br />\nStephy在社交網上載合照，留言：「今天客串電影，跟嘉玲姐、家燕姐和鮑姐三位重量級麻將高手大戰四方城，到底誰勝誰負？」另外，四位美女亦捧着鮮花與導演葉念琛合照。"},{"pid":"a07f5d9eeb32db8d5cdcf44674aed7cea04d78e6","tid":382250,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170831/bkn-20170831202851398-0831_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170831%2Fbkn-20170831202851398-0831_00862_001.html&d=v%2BAlg%2BW9BTXNfQ5RjVNRLW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0f8d54bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170831/bkn-20170831202851398-0831_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7a6e541b33f6af0cd152aba635da1d9147a2e3fb","tid":382250,"uid":62167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score